&lt;p&gt;While working on my &lt;a href=&#34;/post/building-an-arduino-robot-part-i-hardware-components&#34;&gt;Arduino based robot vehicle project&lt;/a&gt; the idea came to me that the Bluetooth module that I&#39;m using as a remote control receiver for my robot would make a great addition to my Raspberry Pi. &lt;/p&gt;
